---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import site from '@/lib/site';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Targeted Health Solutions IV | Menon Medispa | Millburn, NJ"
  description="Targeted health solutions IV therapy in Millburn NJ. Advanced IV formulas for gut health, heart health, pain management, and more."
>
  <main class="sp" data-slug="targeted-health-solutions-iv">

    <section class="sp-hero" aria-label="Targeted Health Solutions IV Therapy">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div class="sp-hero__grid">
          <div class="sp-hero__content">
            <h1 class="sp-hero__title">Targeted Health Solutions IV Therapy</h1>
            <p class="sp-hero__eyebrow">Proactive Nutritional Support for Your Specific Health Journey.</p>
            <p class="sp-hero__lead">Beyond general wellness, our Targeted Health Solutions provide specialized IV formulas designed to offer nutritional support for specific health concerns and conditions. Physician-supervised and evidence-based.</p>
            <div class="sp-hero__actions">
              <a class="sp-btn sp-btn--gold" href="/consultation">Book Your IV Therapy</a>
            </div>
            <div class="sp-reviews">
              <div class="sp-reviews__avatars">
                <img src="/images/90411e0041df.png" alt="Client review" width="44" height="44" />
                <img src="/images/305afeda5f9a.png" alt="Client review" width="44" height="44" />
                <img src="/images/b95880091b44.png" alt="Client review" width="44" height="44" />
              </div>
              <div class="sp-reviews__text">
                <span class="sp-reviews__stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</span>
                <span class="sp-reviews__count">100+ 5 Star Reviews</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <img class="sp-hero__img" src="/images/651c7c197b52.png" alt="Targeted Health Solutions IV Therapy" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-badges" aria-label="Highlights">
      <div class="sp-container sp-badges__row">
        <p class="sp-badge"><span class="sp-badge__check">&#10003;</span> Physician Supervised</p>
        <p class="sp-badge"><span class="sp-badge__check">&#10003;</span> Condition-Specific Formulas</p>
        <p class="sp-badge"><span class="sp-badge__check">&#10003;</span> Evidence-Based</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-plain" aria-label="Formulas">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;">
          <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(1.75rem,3vw,2.25rem);color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 1.5rem;">Choose Your Formula</h2>
          <div style="background:#f8f4f0;padding:1.5rem;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
            <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-xl);color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.4rem;">Gut Health (IBS / UC / Crohn's)</h3>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);font-style:italic;color:#6a6470;margin:0 0 0.75rem;font-size:var(--text-sm);">Nutritional support for gastrointestinal health and inflammation.</p>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0 0 0.75rem;line-height:1.7;">Designed to help manage symptoms of IBS, Ulcerative Colitis, and Crohn's Disease by providing targeted nutrients that support gut lining integrity, reduce inflammation, and restore nutritional deficiencies common in these conditions.</p>
            
          </div><div style="background:#f8f4f0;padding:1.5rem;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
            <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-xl);color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.4rem;">Heart Health / Diabetes Drip</h3>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);font-style:italic;color:#6a6470;margin:0 0 0.75rem;font-size:var(--text-sm);">Metabolic and cardiovascular nutritional support.</p>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0 0 0.75rem;line-height:1.7;">Provides targeted micronutrients including Magnesium, B-vitamins, and antioxidants that support cardiovascular function, glucose metabolism, and reduce oxidative stress associated with metabolic conditions.</p>
            
          </div><div style="background:#f8f4f0;padding:1.5rem;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
            <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-xl);color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.4rem;">Pain Management / Autoimmune</h3>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);font-style:italic;color:#6a6470;margin:0 0 0.75rem;font-size:var(--text-sm);">Anti-inflammatory nutritional support for chronic pain and autoimmune conditions.</p>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0 0 0.75rem;line-height:1.7;">Delivers a high-dose blend of anti-inflammatory nutrients designed to help reduce chronic inflammation and provide nutritional support for autoimmune conditions.</p>
            
          </div><div style="background:#f8f4f0;padding:1.5rem;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
            <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-xl);color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.4rem;">Prenatal / Pregnancy / Fertility</h3>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);font-style:italic;color:#6a6470;margin:0 0 0.75rem;font-size:var(--text-sm);">Specialized nutritional support for preconception and pregnancy.</p>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0 0 0.75rem;line-height:1.7;">Carefully formulated to support fertility, fetal development, and maternal health during pregnancy, providing optimal levels of Folate, B12, Iron, and other essential prenatal nutrients.</p>
            
          </div>
          <p style="margin-top:2rem;"><a class="sp-btn sp-btn--gold" href="/consultation">Schedule Now</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    

    <section class="sp-plain sp-plain--alt" aria-label="Process">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;">
          <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(1.75rem,3vw,2.25rem);color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 1.5rem;">Simple, Relaxing, and Effective</h2>
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;">
            <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;">
              <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-2xl);color:var(--color-accent-warm);flex-shrink:0;line-height:1;">01</span>
              <div><h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.25rem;">Personalized Consultation</h3><p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0;line-height:1.7;">Your session begins with a brief consultation with one of our registered nurses. They will review your wellness goals and answer any questions to ensure your treatment is perfectly suited to your needs.</p></div>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;">
              <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-2xl);color:var(--color-accent-warm);flex-shrink:0;line-height:1;">02</span>
              <div><h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.25rem;">Relax and Recharge</h3><p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0;line-height:1.7;">Once settled in our comfortable therapy lounge, the IV drip is administered. The process is virtually painless and takes about 45-60 minutes. You can relax, read, or catch up on emails while your body absorbs the nutrients.</p></div>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;">
              <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-2xl);color:var(--color-accent-warm);flex-shrink:0;line-height:1;">03</span>
              <div><h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.25rem;">Feel the Benefits</h3><p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0;line-height:1.7;">Many clients report immediate benefits after their session. The nutrients continue to work for days, supporting your body's natural processes and helping you feel and look your best.</p></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    

    <section class="sp-testimonial" aria-label="What Our Clients Say">
      <img class="sp-testimonial__bg" src="/images/30cfb9e87c60.png" alt="" width="1440" height="626" loading="lazy" />
      <div class="sp-testimonial__overlay"></div>
      <div class="sp-container sp-testimonial__inner">
        <h2 class="sp-script-title sp-script-title--light" style="margin-bottom:2rem;">What Our <em>Clients</em> Say</h2>
        <blockquote class="sp-quote">
          <span class="sp-quote__mark">&ldquo;</span>
          Jennifer is amazing. Her aura and energy makes you feel welcomed and comfortable. Love our sessions! And my girl Rose Marie, the receptionist, is just lovely! I always leave with great joy after seeing them.
          <cite>Alexa C.</cite>
        </blockquote>
        <img src="/images/5be44787b3a9.png" alt="5 Star Google Reviews" width="143" height="74" loading="lazy" style="margin-top:1.75rem;" />
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-faq" aria-label="Frequently asked questions">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div class="sp-faq__card">
          <div class="sp-faq__head"><h2 class="sp-faq__title">Frequently asked questions</h2></div>
          <div class="sp-faq__list">
            <details class="sp-faq__item" open>
              <summary>Are Targeted Health Solutions safe?</summary>
              <div class="sp-faq__answer"><p>Yes, but these treatments are performed under physician supervision. Dr. Menon will review your complete medical history, current medications, and specific health conditions before recommending any targeted IV therapy to ensure safety and appropriateness.</p></div>
            </details>
            <details class="sp-faq__item">
              <summary>Can IV therapy replace my current medications?</summary>
              <div class="sp-faq__answer"><p>No. Our Targeted Health Solutions IV therapies are designed to complement your existing medical treatment—not replace it. Always consult with Dr. Menon and your primary care physician before making any changes to your medical regimen.</p></div>
            </details>
            <details class="sp-faq__item">
              <summary>How do I know which targeted solution is right for me?</summary>
              <div class="sp-faq__answer"><p>A consultation with Dr. Menon or our medical team is the first step. We'll review your health history, current symptoms, and goals to determine the most appropriate IV formulation and treatment schedule for your specific needs.</p></div>
            </details>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-cta" aria-label="Explore Targeted Wellness Solutions">
      <div class="sp-container sp-cta__grid">
        <div class="sp-cta__copy">
          <h2 class="sp-cta__title">Explore Targeted Wellness Solutions</h2>
          <p class="sp-cta__sub">Menon Medispa Millburn NJ</p>
          <p>Discuss your specific health goals with Dr. Menon. Schedule your consultation at Menon Medispa in Millburn, NJ today.</p>
          <a class="sp-btn sp-btn--gold" href="/consultation">Schedule Free Consultation</a>
        </div>
        <div class="sp-cta__media">
          <img src="/images/b1a819f35921.webp" alt="Menon Office Staff" width="431" height="560" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</BaseLayout>
